Set Up Your Digital Experience Site

Create an Experience site for your users using the templates provided in the Insurance FSC unmanaged package.

The recommended flow for setting up your Experience site is:

1. Install the Insurance FSC unmanaged package.
2. Create Your Experience Site.
3. Update the Experience Site CSS to ensure that buttons and links display correctly.
4. Hide or Show Components for Mobile to ensure a seamless experience for desktop and mobile users.
5. Save Your Experience Site Template so you can customize the Experience site for your users.
6. Assign Your Template to Your Experience Site and start customizing it to deliver a unique experience to your users.
7. Uninstall the Insurance FSC unmanaged package once you've created your own template.

Publish Your Digital Experience Site.
title: Setting Up a Digital Experience Site for Insurance
